# For a camera mounted on a pan/tilt head):
# Tell the robot where to point the camera by providing a 3D position in robot
# base coordinates.
# Note that this is temporary, and can be overwritten by any new goal.
# Note that there is no guarantee, that the robot will look actually there,
# depening on other currently active goals.

geometry_msgs/PoseStamped target    # 3D point, in robot base coordinates
string reason                       # a string indicating what caught the attention, e.g. "motion", "person", "face"
---
